(16, '350 MM, POWER CUTTER, 2-STROKE ENGINE, 4.8 KW, K 970 RESCUE', '967635601', 39, 48, 16, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Easy and optimal belt tensioning</li>\r\n	<li>Magnesium blade guard</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustable carry strap</li>\r\n	<li>Specially designed starter handle</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>The semi-automatic SmartTension minimizes the risk of under- and over-tensioning.</li>\r\n	<li>It has a magnesium blade guard with decreased weight and reflective decals for high visibility in smoke and water spray, which enhances control of the cutter.</li>\r\n	<li>Enhanced carrying strap and larger carabines for heavy-duty jobs. Allows you to run, walk and climb smoothly with the machine in urgent situations.</li>\r\n	<li>Specially designed starter handle, with room for heavy gloves.</li>\r\n	<li>Sturdy and reliable, it is less sensitive to outer conditions and fuel variations, thanks to the cylinder design and muffler with an integrated heat deflector.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Power Source: Gasoline</li>\r\n	<li>Tank Capacity: 1 Liter</li>\r\n	<li>No. of Engine Stroke: 2</li>\r\n	<li>Output Power: 4.8 kW</li>\r\n	<li>Cylinders: 1</li>\r\n	<li>Blade Diameter: 350 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Arbor Diameter: 25.4 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Cutting Depth: 125 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Blade Thickness: 5 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Peripheral Speed: 90 m/s</li>\r\n	<li>Sound Power Level: 115 dB(A)</li>\r\n	<li>Sound Pressure Level: 104 dB(A)</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrations left/front Handle: 3.8 m/s&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrations right/rear Handle: 4.2 m/s&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 11 kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 965 x 214 x 444 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><a href=\"https://www.aabtools.com/wp-content/uploads/Husqvarna_K-970_Power-Cutters_967348001_Manual-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Husqvarna_K 970 Rescue_Power Cutters_967635601_Manual</a></p>\r\n', 'Husqvarna_K-970-Rescue_967635601_Power-Cutters.png,', '2022-03-22 11:55:15', 1),
(17, '500 MM, FLOOR SAW, 4-STROKE ENGINE, 6.8 KW, FS 410 D', '965150116', 39, 48, 17, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Low vibrations</li>\r\n	<li>Low maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to adjust the blade</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to transport</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustable handles</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Our highly versatile FS 410 D is a compact diesel push floor saw developed with a clear focus on your comfort.</li>\r\n	<li>Ideal for small to mid-sized service and repair jobs in asphalt and concrete. Cuts up to 189 mm deep.</li>\r\n	<li>Engine and blade shaft mounting system increases comfort and gives an excellent cutting performance.</li>\r\n	<li>The IntelliSeal blade shaft system allows for a minimum of 250 maintenance-free hours without daily greasing of bearings.</li>\r\n	<li>Spring-assisted screw feed facilitates blade adjustment in and out of the cut.</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to transport, compact saw that is easy to lift.</li>\r\n	<li>Adjustable handles provide a closer and more comfortable position to the cutting side for easier alignment and straighter cuts. The handle can also be folded for transport</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Power Source: Gasoline</li>\r\n	<li>Tank Capacity: 5.4 Liter</li>\r\n	<li>No. of Engine Stroke: 4</li>\r\n	<li>Output Power: 6.8 kW</li>\r\n	<li>Cylinders: 1 Engine</li>\r\n	<li>Cooling: Air</li>\r\n	<li>Blade Diameter: 500 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Cutting Depth: 189 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Arbor Diameter: 25.4 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Sound Power Level: 108 dB(A)</li>\r\n	<li>Sound Pressure Level: 91 dB(A)</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrations left/front Handle: 4.2 m/s&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrations right/rear Handle: 4.4 m/s&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 165 kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 1557 x 638 x 1084 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><a href=\"https://www.aabtools.com/wp-content/uploads/Husqvarna_FS-410-D_Floor-Saw_965150116_Manual.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Husqvarna_FS 410 D_Floor Saw_965150116_Manual</a></p>\r\n', 'Husqvarna_FS-410-D_965150116-180x180.png,', '2022-03-22 12:02:51', 1),
(18, '600 MM, FLOOR SAW, 4-STROKE ENGINE, 15.5 KW, FS 524', '967046102', 39, 48, 17, 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Self-contained drive system</li>\r\n	<li>Optimal power transmission to the blade</li>\r\n	<li>Low maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to adjust the blade</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Our convenient FS 524 is a powerful, yet compact, self-propelled petrol floor saw ideal for asphalt and concrete cutting.</li>\r\n	<li>Suitable for small to medium-sized service and repair jobs, up to 241 mm cutting depth.</li>\r\n	<li>The optimal power transmission makes it ideal for more demanding jobs, despite its compact size. User-friendly and developed with a clear focus on your comfort.</li>\r\n	<li>Self-propelled for easy operation and comfort.</li>\r\n	<li>Low vibrations engine and blade shaft mounting system increases comfort and gives an excellent cutting performance.</li>\r\n	<li>Self-contained differential drive system eliminating drive gear from rear wheels and related wear. It is simple to handle and maintain.</li>\r\n	<li>Enhanced belt tensioning system gives constant tension without the need for re-tensioning, ensuring optimal performance and increased belt life.</li>\r\n	<li>The IntelliSeal blade shaft system allows for a minimum of 250 maintenance-free hours without daily greasing of bearings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Power Source: Gasoline</li>\r\n	<li>Tank Capacity: 8.3 Liter</li>\r\n	<li>No. of Engine Stroke: 4</li>\r\n	<li>Output Power: 15.5 kW</li>\r\n	<li>Cylinders: 2</li>\r\n	<li>Engine Cooling: Air</li>\r\n	<li>Blade Diameter: 600 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Cutting Depth: 241 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Arbor Diameter: 25.4 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Sound Power Level: 109 dB(A)</li>\r\n	<li>Sound Pressure Level: 88 dB(A)</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrations left/front Handle: 1.8 m/s&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Vibrations right/rear Handle: 2.4 m/s&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 239 kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 1750 x 646 x 1200 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><a href=\"https://www.aabtools.com/wp-content/uploa