(21, '230V, 400 MM MASONRY SAW, 2.2 KW, TS 400 F', '965148101', 39, 48, 18, 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Versatile.&nbsp;Can plunge and bevel cut at 45&deg; or 90&deg; for maximum versatility.</li>\r\n	<li>Efficient slurry sedimentation.&nbsp;The collection tray enables efficient slurry handling for long pump life.</li>\r\n	<li>Sturdy and reliable motor.&nbsp;Provides long product life.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Easy set-up. One person can set up the machine, thanks to the semi-automatic folding legs</li>\r\n	<li>Versatile. Can plunge and bevel cut at 45&deg; or 90&deg; for maximum versatility.</li>\r\n	<li>Efficient slurry sedimentation. The collection tray enables efficient slurry handling for long pump life.</li>\r\n	<li>Sturdy and reliable motor. Provides long product life.</li>\r\n	<li>Heavy duty water pump. The high-quality water pump greatly extends product life.</li>\r\n	<li>Wide-span of cutting depths. The precise height adjustment of the cutter head allows deep step cutting.</li>\r\n	<li>Easy replacement of water pump. Thanks to the electrical quick connection.</li>\r\n	<li>Protected guide rails. The solid frame protects the guide rails from external impact.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Power Source: Electric</li>\r\n	<li>Voltage: 220-230 V</li>\r\n	<li>Frequency: 50-60 Hz</li>\r\n	<li>Rated Input Power: 2.2 kW</li>\r\n	<li>Diameter: 400 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Cutting Depth: 230 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Max. Cutting Length: 700 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 96 kg</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 600 x 600 x 1120 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><a href=\"https://www.aabtools.com/wp-content/uploads/Husqvarna_965148101_Manual_TS-400-F-Masonry-saws.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Husqvarna_965148101_Manual_TS 400 F Masonry saws</a></p>\r\n', 'Husqvarna_965148101_TS-400-F-Masonry-saws.jpg,Husqvarna_965148101_TS-400-F-Masonry-saws-1.jpeg,', '2022-03-22 12:09:50', 1),
