(69, 'LASER ALIGNMENT TOOL', '830/BT', 40, 61, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Single-laser measurement technology means reduced errors from backlash, resulting in better data accuracy</li>\r\n	<li>Intuitive guided user interface quickly and easily completes machine alignments</li>\r\n	<li>Compass measurement mode enables flexible, reliable, and repeatable measurements using an activated electronic inclinometer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>FLUKE 830/BT OFFERS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Single-laser measurement technology means reduced errors from backlash, resulting in better data accuracy</li>\r\n	<li>Intuitive guided user interface quickly and easily completes machine alignments</li>\r\n	<li>Compass measurement mode enables flexible, reliable, and repeatable measurements using an activated electronic inclinometer</li>\r\n	<li>Dynamic machine tolerance check provides continuous evaluation of alignment adjustments, so you know when your machine in acceptable range</li>\r\n	<li>Unique extend mode handles gross misalignment by virtually increasing laser detector size</li>\r\n	<li>Data protection ensures your data is there when you need it, with auto save and resume capability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Applications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Precision alignment</li>\r\n	<li>Rotating shafts</li>\r\n	<li>Maintenance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>FLUKE 830/BT SPECIFICATIONS</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>Computer</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>CPU</td>\r\n			<td>Processor: Intel XScale PXA270 running at 312 MHz<br />\r\n			Memory: 64 MB RAM, 64 MB flash</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Display</td>\r\n			<td>Type: TFT, transmissive (sunlight-readable), 65,535 colors, backlit LED Integrated light sensor for automated adjustment of the brightness to the display according to the lighting conditions &ndash; extends battery life<br />\r\n			Resolution: 320 x 240 pixel; dimensions: 3.5&Prime; (89 mm) diagonal<br />\r\n			Keyboard elements: Setup, measure, diagnose, menu, clear, enter, back keys, navigation cursor cross, alphanumeric keyboard and on/off button</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>LED Indicators</td>\r\n			<td>Multicolor LED for laser status and alignment condition<br />\r\n			Multicolor LED for battery status</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>External Interface</td>\r\n			<td>USB host and USB device (slave)<br />\r\n			Integrated wireless communication, class 1, transmitting power 100 mW<br />\r\n			AC adapter/charger socket</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Environmental Protection</td>\r\n			<td>IP65 (dust proof and water spray resistant), shockproof<br />\r\n			Relative humidity 10 to 90%</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Temperature Range</td>\r\n			<td>Operation: 14 to 122&deg;F (-10 to 50&deg;C)<br />\r\n			Storage: -4 to 140&deg;F (-20 to 60&deg;C)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Battery</td>\r\n			<td>Type: Li-Ion polymer rechargeable battery 7.4 V/2.6 Ah (optimal)<br />\r\n			Operating time: Up to 17 hours (33% measurement, 33% computation, 33% sleep mode)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimensions</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 8.7 x 6.5 x 1.8&Prime; (220 x 165 x 45 mm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 1.64 lbs (742 g)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>Carrying Case</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimensions</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 22.25 x 13.5 x 5&Prime; (565 x 343 x 127 mm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 12.3 lbs (5.6 kg) with all standard parts</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>Reflector (Prism)</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Type</td>\r\n			<td>90&deg; roof prism; accuracy (average): &gt;99%</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Environmental Protection</td>\r\n			<td>IP67 (submersible, dust proof)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Temperature Range</td>\r\n			<td>Operation: -4 to 140&deg;F (-20 to 60&deg;C)<br />\r\n			Storage: -4 to 176&deg;F (-20 to 80&deg;C)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimensions</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 4 x 1.62 x .37&Prime; (100 x 41 x 35 mm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 2.3 oz (65 g)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>sensALIGN 3 Sensor</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Measurement Principle</td>\r\n			<td>Coaxial, reflected laser beam</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>LED Indicators</td>\r\n			<td>1 LED for laser beam status and battery status<br />\r\n			1 LED for wireless communication</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Power Supply</td>\r\n			<td>Battery: Lithium-Ion rechargeable battery 3.7 V/5 Wh<br />\r\n			Operating time: 10 hours (continuous use)<br />\r\n			Charging time: Using charger &ndash; 2.5 hrs for up to 90%; 3.5 hrs for up to 100%; Using USB port &ndash; 3 hrs for up to 90%; 4 hrs for up to 100%</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Environmental Protection</td>\r\n			<td>IP65 (dust proof and water spray resistant), shockproof<br />\r\n			Relative humidity 10 to 90% (non-condensing)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ambient Light Protection</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Temperature Range</td>\r\n			<td>Operation: 14 to 122&deg;F (-10 to 50&deg;C)<br />\r\n			Charging: 32 to 104&deg;F (0 to 40&deg;C)<br />\r\n			Storage: -4 to 140&deg;F (-20 to 60&deg;C)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Detector</td>\r\n			<td>Measurement range: Unlimited, dynamically extendible<br />\r\n			Resolution: 1 &mu;m (0.04 mil) and angular 10 &mu;Rad<br />\r\n			Accuracy (average): &gt;98%</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Inclinometer</td>\r\n			<td>Measurement range: 0 to 360&deg;<br />\r\n			Resolution: 0.1&deg;<br />\r\n			Inclinometer error (Ta = 22&deg;C): +0.3% read out</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Laser</td>\r\n			<td>Type: Semiconductor laser diode<br />\r\n			Wavelength: 630 to 680 nm (red, visible)<br />\r\n			Safety class: Class 2 according to IEC 60825-1:2014<br />\r\n			The laser complies with 21 CFR 1040.10 and 1040.11 except for<br />\r\n			deviations pursuant to Laser Notice No. 50, dated June 24, 2007<br />\r\n			Beam power: &lt;1 mW; Beam divergence: 0.3 mRad</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>External Interface</td>\r\n			<td>Wireless communication</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Transmission Distance</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 98&prime; (30 m) direct line of sight</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimensions</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 4.1 x 2.72 x 2.17&Prime; (105 x 69 x 55 mm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight</td>\r\n			<td>Approximately 7.4 oz (210 g) with dust cap</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.aabtools.com/wp-content/uploads/Fluke-830-Datasheet.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Fluke 830-Datasheet</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.aabtools.com/wp-content/uploads/Fluke-830-Manual.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Fluke 830-Manual</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'FLU_830.jpg,FLU_830-1-1.jpg,FLU_830-2-1.jpg,FLU_830-3-1.jpg,', '2022-03-22 16:51:32'),
